node.text: A YEAR IN THE MAKING 💿✨ NEW ALBUM “Silver Lining II” OUT FRIDAY

I can’t even put into words how emotional today was for me. My old high school asked me to fly back to Florida and be the guest speaker at their graduation 😭🎓 Today will forever remain one of the most memorable days of my life. Congrats again Cypress Bay Class of 2021! Go Lightning ⚡️PS: Scroll to the end to see pics from my graduation 10 years ago lol full speech on YouTube
